{"id":"340001507_One-class_support_vector_classifiers_A_survey","abstract":"Over the past two decades, one-class classification (OCC) becomes very popular due to its diversified applicability in data mining and pattern recognition problems. Concerning to OCC, one-class support vector classifiers (OCSVCs) have been extensively studied and improved for the technology-driven applications; still, there is no comprehensive literature available to guide researchers for future exploration. This survey paper presents an up to date, structured and well-organised review on one-class support vector classifiers. This survey comprises available algorithms, parameter estimation techniques, feature selection strategies, sample reduction methodologies, workability in distributed environment and application domains related to OCSVCs. In this way, this paper offers a detailed overview to researchers looking for the state-of-the-art in this area.","authors":["Shamshe Alam","Sanjay Kumar Sonbhadra","Sonali Agarwal","P. Nagabhushan"],"meta":["March 2020Knowledge-Based Systems 196:105754","DOI:10.1016/j.knosys.2020.105754"],"references":["338423080_A_reduced_universum_twin_support_vector_machine_for_class_imbalance_learning","330706943_RAMD_registry-based_anomaly_malware_detection_using_one-class_ensemble_classifiers","330338189_All-in-one_multicategory_Ramp_loss_maximum_margin_of_twin_spheres_support_vector_machine","324434279_Incremental_Support_Vector_Machine_Combined_with_Ultraviolet-Visible_Spectroscopy_for_Rapid_Discriminant_Analysis_of_Red_Wine","322667929_Efficient_Unsupervised_Parameter_Estimation_for_One-Class_Support_Vector_Machines","322383830_An_Overview_of_Deep_Learning_Based_Methods_for_Unsupervised_and_Semi-Supervised_Anomaly_Detection_in_Videos","322233081_Selecting_training_sets_for_support_vector_machines_a_review","318646668_An_Anomaly_Detection_System_based_on_Variable_N-gram_Features_and_One-Class_SVM","317208190_One-class_support_higher_order_tensor_machine_classif